text: Oleksandr Luchyk (; born 30 March 1994), is a professional Ukrainian football midfielder. ==Career== Luchyk is product of some youth sportive systems, including the FC Illichivets Mariupol sportive school. He signed his contract with FC Illichivets Mariupol in the Ukrainian Premier League in February 2015 and returned to this club after half-year absence. ==References== ==External links== * * Category:1994 births Category:Living people Category:Ukrainian First League players Category:Ukrainian footballers Category:People from Vyzhnytsia Category:PFC Sumy players Category:FC Mariupol players Category:FC Poltava players Category:MFC Mykolaiv players Category:FC Avanhard Kramatorsk players Category:Association football midfielders Category:Ukrainian Premier League players
